title: Jamie Kennedy

description:
My #HoneyDew this week is Jamie Kennedy! The youngest of six kids from Philly, Jamie talks about losing his parents and the pain and guilt that comes with not being able to say goodbye. He also shares a story about being cut from the Brad Pitt movie Ad Astra and some choice HoneyDew Hollywood moments! It's a different side of Jamie Kennedy. Subscribe, download and review!
